dk.itu.jesl.hash

Class CuckooLongKeyHashMap<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dk.itu.jesl.hash.CuckooLongKeyHashMap<V>

  • public final class CuckooLongKeyHashMap<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Cuckoo hashing that uses long (64 bit integer) keys. Does not permit null values. Since keys are not objects, this class does not implement the Map interface, but it provides generic map views that do, via genericMap(LongidFunction idf) and genericMap()
